SafeChat is a open-source secure chat and file transfer program.

SafeChat Built Requirements:
GNU Make
GNU C++ Compiler (g++)
OpenSSL Development Libraries

Build Instructions:
"Cd" to the folder containing the makefile and main.cpp.
Enter "make build" to compile.
Enter "sudo make install" to install SafeChat to /usr/bin/.
Enter "safechat --help" to view the required flags (these flags only need to be provided once, as SafeChat saves the last used preferences).